<div style="max-width: 800px; margin: 40px auto; padding: 0 20px; font-family: sans-serif; color: #333;">
    <h1 style="border-bottom: 2px solid #e91e8c; padding-bottom: 10px; color: #e91e8c;">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p style="color: #888; font-size: 0.9rem;">Last updated: May 2026</p>

    <div style="background: #f9f9f9; border-left: 4px solid #e91e8c; padding: 15px 20px; border-radius: 4px; margin: 20px 0;">
        <p style="margin: 0;">MediConnect is committed to protecting your privacy and handling your medical data with care and transparency.</p>
