    <h3 style="color: #e91e8c;">Information We Collect</h3>
    <p>MediConnect collects personal information such as your name, email address, and medical-related data including appointments and prescriptions in order to provide our services.</p>

    <h3 style="color: #e91e8c;">How We Use Your Information</h3>
    <p>We use your information to manage appointments, send notifications, and display prescription records. We do not sell or share your data with third parties.</p>

    <h3 style="color: #e91e8c;">Data Security</h3>
    <p>We take reasonable measures to protect your personal information. Access to your data is restricted to authorized users only.</p>

    <h3 style="color: #e91e8c;">Your Rights</h3>
    <p>You may request to view, update, or delete your personal data at any time by contacting us.</p>

    <h3 style="color: #e91e8c;">Contact Us</h3>
    <p>If you have any questions about this privacy policy, please contact us at <a href="mailto:support@mediconnect.com" style="color: #e91e8c;">support@mediconnect.com</a>.</p>
</div>